t it exceeds expectations in some native integrations.\n- This marks WeChat’s biggest update ever, blending years of context with AI in a cautious but significant way.", "title": "体验完微信Agent以后，我觉得这就是微信有史以来最大的更新。 "}}}, "card": {"rest_id": "https://t.co/nwjcDiCzEu"}, "cashtag_attachments": [], "core": {"user_results": {"result": {"__typename": "User", "affiliates_highlighted_label": {}, "avatar": {"image_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1756592360367259648/GXJ4Kl6w_normal.jpg"}, "core": {"created_at": "Fri Feb 11 17:55:38 +0000 2022", "name": "数字生命卡兹克", "screen_name": "Khazix0918"}, "dm_permissions": {"can_dm": true}, "follow_request_sent": false, "has_graduated_access": true, "id": "VXNlcjoxNDkyMTk1NTgzNjk5OTUxNjIw", "is_blue_verified": true, "legacy": {"default_profile": true, "default_profile_image": false, "description": "愿我们永远对世界保持好奇。\n公众号：数字生命卡兹克", "entities": {"description": {}}, "fast_followers_count": 0, "favourites_count": 387, "follow_request_sent": false, "followers_count": 55828, "friends_count": 159, "has_custom_timelines": false, "is_translator": false, "listed_count": 613, "media_count": 77, "needs_phone_verification": false, "normal_followers_count": 55828, "notifications": false, "possibly_sensitive": false, "profile_banner_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_banners/1492195583699951620/1768364644", "profile_interstitial_type": "", "statuses_count": 404, "time_zone": "", "translator_type": "none", "url": "", "utc_offset": 0, "want_retweets": false, "withheld_description": "", "withheld_scope": ""}, "location": {"location": ""}, "media_permissions": {"can_media_tag": true}, "parody_commentary_fan_label": "None", "privacy": {"protected": false}, "profile_bio": {"description": "愿我们永远对世界保持好奇。\n公众号：数字生命卡兹克"}, "profile_description_language": "zh", "profile_image_shape": "Circle", "relationship_perspectives": {"blocked_by": false, "blocking": false, "followed_by": false, "following": false, "live_following": false, "muting": false}, "rest_id": "